            Published 10:39 p.m. ET June 23, 2015 | Updated 6:14 p.m. ET June 29, 2015Buy PhotoReception area of the Research and Innovation center in Palo Alto, Tuesday, June 23, 2015.(Photo: Alisa Priddle/Detroit Free Press)Buy Photo
            
